NOTICE — Provenance and attribution
===================================

Original work
-------------
The foundational analyses of this repository were authored by Kai Morales and
published at:

    https://github.com/kaimorales/argentina-worldcup-referee-analysis

Original commits (d5820f8..68f28e0) comprise: the single-tournament Poisson
test (src/analyze.py), the historical-baseline comparison
(src/baseline_comparison.py), the France exposure comparison, scorecard and
placebo control (src/exposure_and_scorecard.py), the 32-team shots-exposure
regression (src/fullfield_regression.py), the structural-break test
(src/structural_break.py), the conspiracy-window scope test
(src/conspiracy_window.py), and the curated datasets and reports they
generate. That work was published without a license; copyright remains with
its author. An issue has been suggested upstream inviting the author to adopt
one.

